   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="abstract" resp="vh">
            <p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_III_4065">* Anno nativitatis ( domini) millesimo
                  quadringentesimo sexagesimo tercio, indictione undecima, die vero sedecima mensis
                  septembris, hora vesperorum aut quasi, pontificatus sanctissimi in Christo patris
                  et domini nostri, domini Pii, divina providencia pape secundi, anno eius sexto ,
                  in Gegenwart des öffentlichen Notars und der Zeugen bestellt <rs type="fn"
                     role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__veit_uczinger_QGW_II_II_3384">Vitus
                        Uczinger, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_stephan-altar_st_maria"
                           >canonicus</roleName> Pataviensis ac rector perpetue misse per olim
                        honestas mulieres, . . <rs type="person" ref="pe__elisabeth_QGW_II_I_613"
                              ><roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__ortolf_lederer_QGW_II_I_613"
                              >relictam</roleName></rs> quondam <rs type="person"
                           ref="pe__ortolf_lederer_QGW_II_I_613">Ortolfi</rs>
                        <roleName type="dead">selig</roleName>, cerdonis, et <rs type="person"
                           ref="pe__ortolf_lederer_QGW_II_I_613">Elisabeth Kolpechkin <roleName
                              type="dead">selig</roleName></rs> et <rs type="person"
                           ref="pe__agnes_QGW_II_II_3331">Agnetem, <roleName type="kin"
                              corresp="pe__hermann_perman_QGW_II_II_2325">relictam</roleName></rs>
                        <rs type="person" ref="pe__hermann_perman_QGW_II_II_2325">Hermanni
                              Perman<roleName type="dead"><add>relictam</add></roleName></rs>
                        <roleName type="dead">selig</roleName>, in <rs type="org"
                           ref="org__wien-st_stephan">ecclesia sancti Stephani</rs>, alias Omnium
                        sanctorum Wienne et in altari beate Marie Virginis fundate</rs></rs> , . . .
                     <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__niklas_de_auln_QGW_II_III_4065"><roleName type="title"
                           >dominum</roleName> Nicolaum de Aulin, <roleName type="title"
                           >baccalaureum formatum in theologia</roleName>, <roleName type="occ"
                           corresp="org__wien-st_stephan">canonicum</roleName> prefate ecclesie
                        sancti Stephani in Wienna , zu seinem <roleName type="rep"
                           corresp="pe__veit_uczinger_QGW_II_II_3384"
                     >Procurator</roleName></rs></rs>, der vor Allem obige <rs type="org"
                     ref="org__wien-st_stephan-altar_st_maria-messe_ledrerin">Messe</rs> dem <rs
                     type="org" ref="org__wien">Bürgermeister und Rathe auflassen</rs> soll. Diese
                  werden sie dem <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_schoenmann_QGW_II_III_4065"
                     >Johannes Schönmann, arcium liberalium <roleName type="prof"
                        >magistro</roleName> alme Universitatis Wiennensis</rs>, verleihen, der ihm
                  dafür den <rs type="org" ref="org__enns-kirche_st_laurenz-altar_st_maria"
                     >Frauen-Altar in der Pfarrkirche des h. Laurentius</rs> zu Enns ausserhalb der
                  Mauern übergibt. </rs></p>
